Titolo: MLB 15: The Show

Anno: 2015

Descrizione: MLB 15: The Show is a Major League Baseball video game developed by San Diego Studio and published by Sony Computer Entertainment. It is the tenth entry of the MLB: The Show franchise, and was released on March 31, 2015, for PlayStation 3, PlayStation 4 and PlayStation Vita.Matt Vasgersian, Eric Karros, and Steve Lyons return as commentators. Mike Carlucci returns as public address announcer. Legends can be used as free agents in the Franchise and Season modes in the game.
On October 31, 2017, Sony decommissioned the game's online servers.

